body:
Thor: brother I got you a present I hope you’ll like it

summary:

Wong: You sure about that?
Stephen: Yes.
Wong: You can come out, Tony!
Tony: *hiding...
body:
Stephen: I’ve got nothing to hide.
Wong: You sure about that?
Stephen: Yes.
Wong: You can come out, Tony!
Tony: *hiding somewhere in the room* You have no proof I’m here!
Wong: There’s are no less than six empty coffee mugs on the table and a whiff of motor grease in the air.
Tony: Circumstantial!

by Ghost (JustAJuxtaposition)

She wished she’d never wandered off or touched that which she should never have touched. But Theodora cannot keep dwelling on the events of the past because she is the daughter of Tony Stark, and their life is all about moving forward. When Pepper Potts inherits the seat at Stark Industries, Theodora becomes acquainted with an eloquent newcomer, and what she knows and has to tell Theodora of herself changes her life forever. Her only hope of keeping any sort of normality in her life or so she is told is to work together with a remarkable group of people.

body:
I’m supposed to post this on Halloween, but I failed to finish on time😂 I guess I’ll not say happy Halloween but an early merry Christmas instead?

I made Tony as Vampire Lord, JARVIS as ghost (because of 3D hologram) and Dummy as Mummy! (Dummy the mummy, just can’t help it~)

What do you guys think they are talking about? I’ll go first:

Tony: J, they must be in awe of my costume.

JARVIS: Absolutely sir. I am sure that they are not just in shock.

summary: Imagine the avengers playing the floor is lava. Peter is on the ceiling, Stephen is floating because of his cloak. Clint climbs...
body: Imagine the avengers playing the floor is lava. Peter is on the ceiling, Stephen is floating because of his cloak. Clint climbs the highest thing he can find. Steve sitting on the table. Thor standing confused by this game but plays anyway, And Tony throws himself on the floor. And you can hear from across the room “tony no” and tony without moving just goes “Tony yes”. And peter just uses his webs and sticks tony to the way saying “thats better” nat walks in and calls them idiots then leaves

-Tony has to do summer school because he skipped too many days of...
body:
Summer Au:

-Peter is in summer school but it’s for university

-Tony has to do summer school because he skipped too many days of school

-Tony asks Peter for help

-Peter says no because hes too busy and Tony’s flirtatious

-Peter soon gives in when Tony offers to pay him 500 dollars each session.

-Peter finding Tony annoying

-And Tony purposely annoying him just because he thinks Annoyed Peter is cute.
